OL,3,CGuernsey and Jersey paying up to #1m a
OL,4,Cmonth for contingency ferry plans
OL,6,FGuernsey and Jersey have reportedly
OL,7,Fbeen paying up to #1,000,000 a month
OL,8,Fto keep two vessels on standby in
OL,9,FDunkirk to provide sea links to the
OL,10,Fislands for almost a year.
OL,12,FIt's thought that both islands are
OL,13,Fsplitting the cost of keeping the
OL,14,Fvessels on contingency, paying up to
OL,15,F#500,000 each monthly.
