OL,3,CGuernsey and Jersey paying up to #1m a
OL,4,Cmonth for contingency ferry plans
OL,6,FWhen asked about the plans, which were
OL,7,Fput in place following Condor's
OL,8,Fannouncement about temporary financial
OL,9,Ftrouble in December 2023, Deputy
OL,10,FKirsten Morel said it's certainly
OL,11,F'costing' the islands.
OL,13,FHe said: "At the moment we do have
OL,14,Fcontingency plans. That is something
OL,15,Fthat's been the case for all of this
OL,16,Fyear so far. The reality is we have
OL,17,Ffreight contingency plans so we have
OL,18,Fvessels that are on contingency and
OL,19,Fcan be pulled down at a moments notice.
