OL,3,CGuernsey and Jersey paying up to #1m a
OL,4,Cmonth for contingency ferry plans
OL,6,F"Both islands are paying for those
OL,7,Fcontingency vessels. It is certainly
OL,8,Fcosting us."
OL,10,FWhen asked about Condor's financial
OL,11,Ftroubles and if this impacted
OL,12,FGuernsey's decision to pick Brittany
OL,13,FFerries, who recently purchased a
OL,14,Fmajority share hold in the company,
OL,15,FDeputy Neil Inder explained how the
OL,16,Fplans came about.
