OL,3,CGuernsey and Jersey paying up to #1m a
OL,4,Cmonth for contingency ferry plans
OL,6,FReferencing a trip he made to Scotland
OL,7,Fwith Morel last December, he said:
OL,8,F"There's no two ways about it. In
OL,9,FDecember of last year, Condor released
OL,10,Fa statement stating that it was having
OL,11,Ftemporary financial difficulty.
OL,13,F"Guernsey and Jersey met as friends,
OL,14,Fwe had a joint problem. When your life
OL,15,Fline sea links tells you they've got a
OL,16,Fproblem, you've got to find a solution.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
