OL,3,CGuernsey and Jersey paying up to #1m a
OL,4,Cmonth for contingency ferry plans
OL,6,F"That trip was probably one of the
OL,7,Fmost worrying days of my political
OL,8,Fcareer, because right then with Condor
OL,9,Funder the old brand and old structure,
OL,10,Fwe weren't too sure if the Vessels
OL,11,Fwere going to make Christmas."
OL,13,FIt's unclear if this arrangement will
OL,14,Fend when the new deal is confirmed by
OL,15,Fboth islands or what the exact figure
OL,16,Fis that's been paid so far is.
