OL,3,CGuernsey and Jersey paying up to #1m a
OL,4,Cmonth for contingency ferry plans
OL,6,FIt comes as Guernsey named Brittany
OL,7,FFerries as their preferred ferry
OL,8,Fservice provider for the next 15
OL,9,Fyears. Jersey are yet to confirm its
OL,10,Fdecision, but Neil Inder says Guernsey
OL,11,Fisn't trying to force Jersey's hand.
